== Usage ==

<code>{{tlx|Background color|red|Hello, world!}}</code> results in {{Background color|red|Hello, world!}}<br/>
<code><nowiki>{{bgcolor|#00F000|Hello, world!}}</nowiki></code> results in {{Background color|#00F000|Hello, world!}}

See [[Web colors]] for a list of colors.

